Arlette Merry https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arlette_Merry 0 Arlette Merry (18 March 1918 – 19 February 2015) was a French actress and singer. She was the daughter of Lucien Pinoteau and the sister of Claude Pinoteau and Jacques Pinoteau. Merry died in February 2015 at the age of 96.
